text: Kevin Michael McHale (born June 14, 1988) is an American actor and singer. He got his start playing Dooley Fibadoo on Zoey 101. He is known for his role as Artie Abrhams on the Fox television show, Glee. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Texas Category:People from Plano, Texas
title: Kevin McHale (actor)
